 Agent\", role: \"Traces customer queries and guides them to correct product answers.\" }\n 21 | ];\n 22 | \n 23 | export default function BankingPage() {\n 24 |   const [demoOutput, setDemoOutput] = useState(\"Select a query option below to test the Banking Knowledge Agent.\");\n 25 |   const [running, setRunning] = useState(false);\n 26 | \n 27 |   const triggerQuery = (type: string) => {\n 28 |     setRunning(true);\n 29 |     if (type === \"policy\") {\n 30 |       setDemoOutput(\"Searching mortgage rules database for 'LTV limits on secondary homes'...\");\n 31 |       setTimeout(() => {\n 32 |         setDemoOutput(\"FOUND: Mortgage Section 4.2. Secondary home limit is 80% LTV, requiring a minimum credit score of 720. Audit Trail: SOC-2 Verified.\");\n 33 |         setRunning(false);\n 34 |       }, 700);\n 35 |     } else {\n 36 |       setDemoOutput(\"Auditing commercial loan file #9410A for 'interest rate indexing provisions'...\");\n 37 |       setTimeout(() => {\n 38 |         setDemoOutput(\"FOUND: Page 14. SOFR index peg with 150bps margin. Human audit checkpoint triggered for risk approval.\");\n 39 |         setRunning(false);\n 40 |       }, 700);\n 41 |     }\n 42 |   };\n 43 | \n 44 |   return (\n 45 |     <InnerPageShell>\n 46 |       <InnerPageHero\n 47 |         category=\"Vertical Solutions\"\n 48 |         title=\"Enterprise Banking Cognitive Layers\"\n 49 |         highlightedWord=\"Banking\"\n 50 |         description=\"Connect core mainframes with conversational AI interfaces, policy retrieval networks, and relationship copilots.\"\n 51 |         breadcrumbs={[{ label: \"Industries\", href: \"/industries\" }, { label: \"Banking\" }]}\n 52 |       />\n 53 | \n 54 |       <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 pb-16\">\n 55 |         <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">Challenge Landscape</h2>\n 56 |         <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4\">\n 57 |           {CHALLENGES.map((c, i) =