umentation tasks to secure pre-configured agents.\" },\n 85 |               { id: \"audit\", name: \"Immutable Audit Registry\", desc: \"Records compound searches and regulatory pre-assessments.\" }\n 86 |             ].map((tab) => (\n 87 |               <button\n 88 |                 key={tab.id}\n 89 |                 onClick={() => setActiveTab(tab.id)}\n 90 |                 className={`w-full p-3 rounded-xl text-left border text-xs transition-all ${\n 91 |                   activeTab === tab.id ? \"bg-white/5 border-white/10 text-white\" : \"border-transparent text-white/50 hover:text-white\"\n 92 |                 }`}\n 93 |               >\n 94 |                 <span className=\"font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">{tab.name}</span>\n 95 |                 {activeTab === tab.id && <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/60 leading-normal font-light mt-1\">{tab.desc}</p>}\n 96 |               </button>\n 97 |             ))}\n 98 |           </div>\n 99 |         </div>\n100 | \n101 |         <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/40 backdrop-blur-[12px] flex flex-col items-center\">\n102 |           <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4\">Interactive Life Sciences Architecture Blueprint</span>\n103 |           <div className=\"w-full max-w-[420px] h-[280px] relative\">\n104 |             <svg className=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 340\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n105 |               <path d=\"M250 40 L250 110 M250 150 L250 200 M250 240 L250 290\" stroke=\"url(#pipeGlow)\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeDasharray=\"6 4\" />\n106 |               <g onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"gateway\")} className=\"cursor-pointer\">\n107 |                 <rect x=\"100\" y=\"20\" width=\"300\" height=\"40\" rx=\"8\" fill={activeTab === \"gateway\" ? \"#009DFF\" : \"#0A0A0C\"} stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n108 |                 <text