b-2\">Evidence Indexing Speed</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">Reduce file categorization and preliminary cross-checks from multiple days of manual searching to near-instantaneous search layers.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/60\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase mb-2\">Checklist Workflow Consistency</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">Enforce programmatic check consistency across hundreds of client record sets, flagging minor anomalies instantly.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/60\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase mb-2\">Complete Verification Log</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">Maintain solid, SOC-2 compliant transaction traces for every query, preserving the chain of human accountability.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Related Capabilities */}\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 pb-16 border-t border-white/5 pt-12\">\n        <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4\">Related Capabilities & Platforms</h3>\n        <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\">\n          {[\"Foundry Visual Studio\", \"Private Vector Memory\", \"Secure Ledger Gateway\", \"Continuous Auditing\"].map((cap, i) => (\n            <span key={i} className=\"px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-xs text-white/70\">{cap}</span>\n          ))}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 pb-16\">\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Architect Your Private Audit Cognitive Layer\"\n          description=\"Consult with our systems engineers to outline secure document mirrors, zero-cache gate