60 leading-relaxed mb-4\">Simulate local, sandboxed review of contracts and matters. No data is stored outside the immediate session context.</p>\n          <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n            <button onClick={() => runDemo(\"contract\")} disabled={running} className=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-white text-black\">Audit Liability Clauses</button>\n            <button onClick={() => runDemo(\"precedent\")} disabled={running} className=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white\">Search Case Precedents</button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 min-h-[120px] flex flex-col justify-between font-mono\">\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 block border-b border-white/5 pb-1 uppercase tracking-wider\">LEGAL REPOSITORY LOGS</span>\n          <p className=\"text-xs text-green-400 my-2\">{log}</p>\n          <span className=\"text-[8px] text-white/30 text-right\">LEGAL CONTEXT // SECURE MEMORY</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 pb-12\">\n        <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Outcome Levers</h2>\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n          <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/60\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase mb-1\">Contract Risk Mitigation</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">Programmatically flag non-standard provisions and liability deviations across active deal rooms.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/60\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase mb-1\">Matter Synthesis Velocity</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">Construct comprehensive chronological 